Netvibes.org  preview4-alpha change logs

* Exposition PHP Library
- Migrate source from /library/php to /library/Exposition
- Rewrite Makefile (doc, php-syntax, php-phpunit, php-qa, php-phpcs, php-phpcpd)
- Add documentation generator (using doxygen)
- Implement UnitTest Environments
- Implement PHP Quality Assurance Test Environment
- Clean PHP Class NameSpace
- Rename Exposition Classe to Exposition_Load and remove NV_* constants in all files
- Add Exposition_Archive to generate Widget package using more compression format
- Add Exposition_Proxy ajax/json/feed proxy features
- Add Exposition_Controller_Widget/Proxy to implement Exposition in your Zend MVC instance.
- Clean PHP source code
- Add Exposition_Compiler: Desktop_Screenlets, Desktop_Vista, Blogger
- Add Exposition_Compiler draft: Desktop_Chrome, Desktop_Kludget, Desktop_FireFox, Desktop_Jil
- Fix Exposition_Parser_Uwa
- Remove Netvibes dependencies
- A Object param proxy support for Json variable name (useful for cross-domain ajax request issue required by some Compiler)

